                <mxCell id="shape-5" value="The purpose of this workbook (and the associated Word and PowerPoint templates) is to demonstrate how theExcel-to-Word Document Automation Add-Incan update a variety of common financial tables.Thisdocument focuses on financial tables. The add-in can also update other content types. See the add-in and https://analysisplace.com for details.Sample Documents | AnalysisPlace" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
